dc_description_s: This data represents zoning (general) for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2021. [This layer depicts the various zoning types, as dictated by the Shawano County Planning, Development, and Zoning Department. The layer contains data for those areas that fall under county zoning jurisdiction and depicts areas not under county zoning jurisdiction.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
